snippet.title: Rally Point 2 Trailer
snippet.description:
Play it here: http://www.agame.com/game/rally-point-2.html

Rally Point 2 is a sequel to the popular race game Rally Point, originally released on several game portals in 2009. Rally Point 2 has all the good stuff of its predecessor and combines this with new tracks, more cars and exciting challenges!
